---
import Icon from "../Icon.astro";
---

<section data-cg-screen="result" hidden>
  <div class="card text-center py-10 px-6 sm:px-10 border-l-4 border-brand-orange min-w-0">
    <div class="mx-auto flex items-center justify-center w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-brand-orange-light text-brand-orange-dark mb-4">
      <Icon name="check" class="w-7 h-7" />
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-soft" data-cg-result-heading tabindex="-1">あなたの相談先はこちら</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-ink [overflow-wrap:break-word]" data-cg-result-name></p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-ink-soft leading-relaxed [overflow-wrap:break-word]" data-cg-result-summary></p>

    <dl class="mt-6 max-w-sm mx-auto space-y-4 border-t border-black/10 pt-6 text-left">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <Icon name="phone" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-brand-orange-dark" />
        <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
          <dt class="text-xs font-bold text-ink-soft">電話番号</dt>
          <dd class="min-w-0">
            <a href="#" data-cg-phone-link class="hidden text-lg font-bold text-ink underline [overflow-wrap:anywhere]"></a>
            <span data-cg-phone-unknown class="text-ink-soft">確認中</span>
          </dd>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <Icon name="clock" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-brand-orange-dark" />
        <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
          <dt class="text-xs font-bold text-ink-soft">受付時間</dt>
          <dd class="text-ink-soft [overflow-wrap:break-word]" data-cg-hours>確認中</dd>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden items-start gap-3" data-cg-location-row>
        <Icon name="location" class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-brand-orange-dark" />
        <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
          <dt class="text-xs font-bold text-ink-soft">場所</dt>
          <dd class="text-ink-soft [overflow-wrap:break-word]" data-cg-location></dd>
        </div>
      </div>
    </dl>

    <div class="mt-6 rounded-xl bg-brand-orange-light/50 px-4 py-3 text-left">
      <p class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-ink">
        <Icon name="document" class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
        <span>組織変更などにより担当窓口が変更される場合があります。来庁前に、お電話または延岡市公式ホームページでご確認ください。</span>
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-ink-soft" data-cg-last-confirmed hidden></p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap items-stretch sm:items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="#" data-cg-phone-button hidden class="btn-primary justify-center">
        <Icon name="phone" class="w-5 h-5" />
        電話する
      </a>
      <a href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-secondary justify-center" data-cg-official-link hidden>
        <Icon name="external-link" class="w-4 h-4" />
        公式ページを見る
        <span class="sr-only">（新しいタブで開く・外部サイト）</span>
      </a>
      <button type="button" class="btn-secondary justify-center" data-cg-restart>
        最初からやり直す
      </button>
      <button type="button" class="btn-secondary justify-center" data-cg-show-list>
        一覧から探す
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
